{
    "m_SGVersion": 0,
    "m_Type": "UnityEditor.ShaderGraph.StickyNoteData",
    "m_ObjectId": "5cb7d8505771452193655dcced1a5f5d",
    "m_Title": "What and How",
    "m_Content": "Shader combines existing paint and new one\nTakes UV coordinates and brush radius to add circle in those coorinates with that radius\n\nMainTex is what is changed.\nOutputs red as it's used in the Wall shader to display paint opacity\nShould be used with Blit.",
